{"title":"绿","authors":["康志强"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":10,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"康志强"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿了椰林，绿了蕉园；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿了土地，绿了峰巅；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿了大海，绿了高天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿藤盖着房顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿叶遮着海南；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连空气都流着绿的芳香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海南啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你这样恬静，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样安然！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能相信你地处国境前沿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却到处是静谧的笑脸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我环顾四周寻求答案——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然，绿色在我眼前闪动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是解放军的衣衫！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿了椰林，绿了蕉园……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色是和平的伙伴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色是人们的生命线……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}